articles.title: Oscar Pistorius released from South Africa prison after serving 9 years for murdering girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp - CNN
articles.description: The double-amputee sprinter was released from prison on Friday, more than a decade after shooting girlfriend Reeva Steenkamp in a killing that shocked the world.
articles.content:
Johannesburg, South AfricaCNN
